
Ranger Help for: terrains
=========================

SUMMARY:
Different terrains are found all over the realms of Darkwind. Rangers
will move through many of them, and Rangers are not penalized just for
fighting or exploring outside their primary and secondary terrains.

Primary and secondary terrain still matter. They improve a Ranger's
footing in combat and can influence the cost, cooldown, damage, or feel
of many Ranger skills. Some skills also require a specific kind of land.

Use 'rhelp <terrain>' to read about a specific terrain.

EXAMPLES:
  rhelp forest
  rhelp desert
  rhelp mountain
  rhelp dock

TERRAINS:
  forest       plains       swamp        desert       jungle
  hills        beach        arctic       barren       underground
  mountain     city         sea          lake         river
  road         dock         inside       underwater   outside

